WEBVTT

00:00:01.262 --> 00:00:03.412
June 8, 2010,

00:00:04.444 --> 00:00:08.180
Russell Wilson, fourth-round pick
to the Colorado Rockies baseball.

00:00:08.204 --> 00:00:09.364
I'm fired up,

00:00:09.388 --> 00:00:11.243
one of the highest moments of my life.

00:00:11.267 --> 00:00:14.450
Every kid's dream to be drafted
by a Major League Baseball team.

00:00:14.474 --> 00:00:15.878
June 8, 2010.

00:00:16.639 --> 00:00:18.134
June 9, 2010 --

00:00:19.149 --> 00:00:21.243
(Imitating flatline sound)

00:00:21.855 --> 00:00:23.122
The line goes flat.

00:00:23.696 --> 00:00:24.963
My dad passes away.

00:00:26.967 --> 00:00:28.347
The highest of the high

00:00:28.371 --> 00:00:29.803
to the lowest of the low.